<h1 align="center">Bitscrape</h1>

<p align="center">
  <a href="https://pypi.org/project/bitscrape/">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/bitscrape.svg">
  </a>
  <a href="https://pypi.org/project/bitscrape/">
